    </script>     
    <script src=
"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js">
    </script>     
    <script src=
"https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js">
    </script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="jumbotron text-center" style="color:white; background-color: #3399ff">
  <h2>Help Page</h2>
</div>

<div style="margin-left: 2%">
<h6>This page will show you how to utilize this app to the fullest.</h6>

<h2 style="color:#3399ff">Admins</h2>
<h3>Authorizing an Admin Account</h3>
<h6>To authorize an admin account, the user must first create a normal account and an admin must give them admin privileges.</h6>
<h6>To give admin privileges, log into the admin account and select "Make Admin" inside of the home page.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Admin.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 
<h3>Delete Members Accounts</h3>
<h6>To delete a member's account, an admin must click on the "Destroy" button on the home page (shown in screenshot above).</h6>

<h3>Setting Up Milestones</h3>
<h6>To add a milestone, the admin must first select "View Milestones".</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/View Milestones.png", style: "width:20%;height:20%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h6>  Then select "New Milestone". In this page, the current milestones can be seen, modified, and deleted as well.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/New Milestone.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h6>After filling out the fields, the admin can click "Create Milestone"</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Create Milestone.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>Create/Modify/Delete Events</h3>
<h6>To create a new event, go to the "View Events" page and select "New Event".</h6>
<h6>This page also allows to see the current events, modify events, and delete events as well</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/View Events.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h6>To create a new event, fill out the fields. The meeting code will be autogenerated and shown right after creating.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/New Event.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>Reset Points</h3>
<h6>To reset points, click on the "Reset Points" button on the homepage. This will reset all of the members' and admins' points back to 0</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Reset Points.png" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h6>After clicking reset points, the admin must enter their email to confirm.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Reset Confirm.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h2 style="color:#3399ff">Users</h2>

<h3>Creating an Account</h3>
<h6>To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button on the home page.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/loginsignup.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h6>Fill out the corresponding fields and click "Sign Up".</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Signup.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>Points</h3>
<h6>To see the number of current points, log into your user account. </h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Points.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>View Event Schedule</h3>
<h6>To view the current events, click on "View Events" in the user's homepage.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/View Events.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>View Leaderboard</h3>
<h6>To view the leaderboard of the current users with the highest points, click on "Leaderboard".</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/View Leaderboard.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<h3>View Milestones</h3>
<h6>To view the milesetones that the current user has reached, select "My Milestones" Milestones can be created by admins (as shown above).</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/My Milestones.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 


<h3>Attending a Meeting</h3>
<h6>To attend a meeting and get credit, add the Event ID in the provided field. Upon providing the correct Event ID (and assuming that the timing is still valid, this will lead to a new page with the event information.</h6>
<%= image_tag "help/Meeting Validation.png", style: "width:50%;height:50%;" %>
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p></p> 

<div class="text-center">
<%= button_to 'Back', root_path, :class => "btn btn-light", :method => :get  %>
</div>
</div>
</body>
